[Apologies to anyone seeing this twice.]

Theoretically-inclined readers of sci.crypt might be interested in
the article with that title in JACM 40:1 (January 1993), pp. 17-47
by Dolev, Dwork, Waarts & Yung.  It significantly extends
the Rabin & Ben-Or work on verifiable secret sharing.

